  "title": "如何查看运动或睡眠月统计数据？",
  "answer": " <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt; \">1.     查看运动信息。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:0cm;\">运动过程中您可以上下滑动手环屏幕查看运动信息。</p> <table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"431\" style=\"width:323.45pt;margin-left:29.25pt;border-collapse:collapse;\"> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"144\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:107.8pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\"> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:center;line-height:normal\" align=\"center\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084631558001.png)</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:center;line-height:normal\" align=\"center\">走路</p> </td> <td width=\"144\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:107.8pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\"> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:center;line-height:normal\" align=\"center\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084632864002.png)</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:center;line-height:normal\" align=\"center\">跑步</p> </td> <td width=\"144\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:107.85pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\"> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:center;line-height:normal\" align=\"center\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084632985003.png)</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:center;line-height:normal\" align=\"center\">卡路里</p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:0cm;\">**说明：**手环屏幕上跑步图标默认不显示，如果您有跑步运动时会显示出来。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:0cm;\">您也可以连接手环和手机，通过手机APP查看运动数据。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt; line-height:normal\" align=\"center\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084632110004.jpg)</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt; \">2.     查看月度统计数据。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:0cm;\">在APP中点击运动/睡眠数据界面，点击数据界面底部月统计图标，查看月度统计数据。</p> <p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-align: center;text-indent:0cm;\" align=\"center\">![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084632629005.jpg)</p>",
